## Overview

Sangha Innovation Tank presents **four complementary AI agent solutions** designed to transform district-level health operations by automating critical workflows, improving data quality, and freeing health workers to focus on patient care.

### ğŸ¯ Four Solutions

1. **AI Agent for District Program Managers (DPM)**
   - Automated campaign planning (3-4 weeks â†’ 30 minutes)
   - Real-time micro-plan generation
   - Role-based task assignments
   - Live analytics dashboard

2. **AI Agent for Mid Managers - Data & Compliance Reporting**
   - Continuous health indicator monitoring
   - Auto-generated reports (weekly, monthly, quarterly)
   - Compliance verification (DISHA, ABHA)
   - Action Taken Report (ATR) tracking

3. **DigiPanjiyan - ABHA Registration Agent**
   - Touch-screen patient registration kiosk
   - Instant ABHA generation (2-3 minutes)
   - Duplicate detection and prevention
   - Staff analytics dashboard

4. **SAARTHI - Smart Assisted Health Intelligence**
   - Voice-first health data capture
   - Real-time AI transcription
   - Automatic health record generation
   - Batch processing and analytics

