## ğŸš€ Quick Start

### Prerequisites
- Node.js 16+ (for frontend)
- Python 3.8+ (for backend)
- Git

### Installation

```bash
# Clone repository
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/sangha-innovation-tank.git
cd sangha-innovation-tank

# Frontend setup
npm install

# Backend setup
cd backend
pip install -r requirements.txt
cd ..
```

### Running Locally

**Frontend:**
```bash
npm start
# Opens http://localhost:3000
```

**Backend:**
```bash
cd backend
python app.py
# Starts at http://localhost:5000
```

**Access Dashboard Portal:**
Navigate to http://localhost:3000 and select any dashboard:
- [DPM Campaign Manager](http://localhost:3000/dashboards/dpm-campaign)
- [Data Reporting Agent](http://localhost:3000/dashboards/data-reporting)
- [DigiPanjiyan Registration](http://localhost:3000/dashboards/digipanjiyan)
- [SAARTHI Health Intelligence](http://localhost:3000/dashboards/saarthi)

