## ğŸ¨ Design System

All dashboards follow a unified design system:

- **Color Palette:** Professional healthcare theme
  - Primary: Teal (#208080)
  - Background: Cream/Light (#F5F5F5)
  - Status: Green (success), Yellow (warning), Red (critical)

- **Typography:** System fonts with fallbacks
- **Layout:** Responsive grid (mobile-first)
- **Accessibility:** WCAG 2.1 AA compliant

See [Design System Documentation](./assets/css/design-system.css)

## ğŸ”§ Technology Stack

**Frontend:**
- HTML5, CSS3, Vanilla JavaScript (no frameworks)
- Responsive design (mobile-first)
- Real-time data updates with WebSockets
- Accessible components (ARIA labels, keyboard navigation)

**Backend:**
- Python 3.8+
- Flask (lightweight web framework)
- SQLite/PostgreSQL (data storage)
- RESTful API design

**Deployment:**
- GitHub Pages (static frontend)
- AWS/Azure/Heroku (backend hosting)
- Docker containerization
- GitHub Actions CI/CD

