## ğŸš¢ Deployment Options

### Option 1: GitHub Pages (Frontend Only)
```bash
npm run build
npm run deploy
```

### Option 2: Heroku (Full Stack)
```bash
heroku create sangha-innovation-tank
git push heroku main
```

### Option 3: Docker (Containerized)
```bash
docker build -t sangha-innovation-tank .
docker run -p 3000:3000 -p 5000:5000 sangha-innovation-tank
```

See [Deployment Guide](./docs/DEPLOYMENT.md) for detailed instructions.

## ğŸ“Š Dashboard Features

### DPM Campaign Manager
- Campaign creation with AI-generated micro-plans
- Real-time analytics (enrollment, screening, referrals)
- Role-based task assignments
- Daily progress updates (email/SMS/WhatsApp examples)

### Data Reporting Agent
- Real-time health indicator monitoring
- Auto-generated compliance reports
- ATR tracking and escalation
- AI agent activity dashboard

### DigiPanjiyan Registration
- Bilingual touch-screen interface
- Simulated biometric authentication
- Instant ABHA generation
- Registration analytics by time period

### SAARTHI Health Intelligence
- Real-time voice transcription
- Medical data extraction
- Digital Health Record generation
- Batch processing analytics

